---
title: Middle Eastern Lamb Koftas & Cos Salad with Garlicky Sour Cream & Mint
description: Spiced to perfection and packed with flavour, these Middle Eastern lamb koftas are a feast for the senses! Served with a crisp cos salad, cooling garlic sour cream, and fresh mint, every bite is a delicious balance of warmth and freshness. A vibrant dish that’s as satisfying as it is simple!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
